messages.text: U hear about this new text message chain?
It’s ten messages actual people sent right before they died.
Do you want me to forward it?
Come on. Ur not the least bit curious?
One of them was completely shocking.
1. R u there? 2. Don’t let them do this. 3. Please!!! 4. I don’t see anything. 5. About to. 6. I can’t. 7. It was him. 8. I love you. 9. Soon I will be too.
Wow. I didn’t really need that.
Wait. Where’s number 10? Didn’t you say ten?
I did. I’m so sorry Jen.
There’s only nine because, unless you send this to someone else… Someone who willingly accepts it.
You have twenty-four hours. I’m really sorry.
No. It’s for real. These are the last nine people who didn’t manage to send it to anyone else.
It’s real and you better start trying to find someone who hasn’t heard of it already or you’re next.
Jen. Don’t wait. Find someone to accept the message.
Did I tell you what happened last night?
You know Aubrey, from our stats class?
Yeah. HER. She texts me out of the blue and asks me if I want to read this list.
It’s like a list of things peopled texted right before they died.
Right? So, I don’t know why, but I said yes.
And she’s like, now you have to send it to someone else in 24 hours or you’ll end up on the list.
Did you send it to anyone?
It’s just a stupid game, right?
This is totally a thing. People totally believe this is real.
No. Still. Maybe you should send it to SOMEONE.
Do you want me to send it to you?
Well, if you are I have just the study break for you. ;).
Uh, all right. Tell me more. ;).
It’s a list of things people texted right before they died.
Ok… I’d want to read this, why?
No. I just don’t want to read it.
R u sure? Because u sound scared.
Why do you care so much if I read it?
U want to come over and help me study?
Will you read the list if I do?
This is so annoying. Do u think she made it up?
It’s literally all over the internet.
It’s probably a hoax. But supposedly there’s been a rise in deaths at colleges.
U need to find someone gullible fast.
Great. How are things at home?
The same. Mom is grading papers and Dad is watching TV.
I have my driver’s test on Tuesday.
Nice. Hey. Did you hear about this list people are sending around?
It’s just the last text messages people sent before they died.
Do u want to read it?
Never mind. I can’t find it. Good luck on your test.
Bummer. Well, guess we’ll find out if it’s a hoax or not.
Do u want me to come over?
Then I’ll stay on the phone.
It’s weird. I know it’s not real but I feel…
You’re just scared by all this. Has it been  24 hours yet?
Jen. Come on. Don’t be weird.
Hey man. Here’s that list I told you about. It’s cool to send, right?
1. Don’t let them do this. 2. Please!!! 3. I don’t see anything. 4. About to. 5. I can’t. 6. It was him. 7. I love you. 8. Soon I will be too. 9. Just about.
